  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/eb899081f19402d86424d6bbf6b97900.poster.avif?t=1760799085\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/eb899081f19402d86424d6bbf6b97900.webm?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/eb899081f19402d86424d6bbf6b97900.mp4?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you take the role of a heroine named Janet in a medical complex where a corporation hires her to do dirty work under the guise of research. However, it soon becomes apparent that something is not right here. Janet and her childhood friend decide to escape from this place. During their adventure, the heroines encounter hostile robots, cyborgs, drones and humans. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/d7d8316d2dbb5fd12d9f981f327b971a.poster.avif?t=1760799085\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/d7d8316d2dbb5fd12d9f981f327b971a.webm?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/d7d8316d2dbb5fd12d9f981f327b971a.mp4?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In your arsenal there are light and heavy weapons with different characteristics and principles of action. You can use the environment in firefights to gain an advantage over your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/0901b87e96c14c66a77a925333f8afe2.poster.avif?t=1760799085\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/0901b87e96c14c66a77a925333f8afe2.webm?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/0901b87e96c14c66a77a925333f8afe2.mp4?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By destroying enemies, you gain experience and credits, which you can use to pump up your characteristics and buy items.Improving your character is an important part of your adventure. With enhanced skills, you'll be able to take down enemies faster, hack weapon crates, earn more credits, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/ec54c5c47148aa0c410ed91ab057a2b5.poster.avif?t=1760799085\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/ec54c5c47148aa0c410ed91ab057a2b5.webm?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/ec54c5c47148aa0c410ed91ab057a2b5.mp4?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dexterity is your middle name, and on the battlefield you'll have to show it to the fullest, dodging enemy fire. Use swipes and jumps to outsmart the enemy and come at him from behind, and then victory will be yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/eb899081f19402d86424d6bbf6b97900.poster.avif?t=1760799085\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/eb899081f19402d86424d6bbf6b97900.webm?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/eb899081f19402d86424d6bbf6b97900.mp4?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you take the role of a heroine named Janet in a medical complex where a corporation hires her to do dirty work under the guise of research. However, it soon becomes apparent that something is not right here. Janet and her childhood friend decide to escape from this place. During their adventure, the heroines encounter hostile robots, cyborgs, drones and humans. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/d7d8316d2dbb5fd12d9f981f327b971a.poster.avif?t=1760799085\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/d7d8316d2dbb5fd12d9f981f327b971a.webm?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/d7d8316d2dbb5fd12d9f981f327b971a.mp4?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In your arsenal there are light and heavy weapons with different characteristics and principles of action. You can use the environment in firefights to gain an advantage over your enemies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/0901b87e96c14c66a77a925333f8afe2.poster.avif?t=1760799085\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/0901b87e96c14c66a77a925333f8afe2.webm?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/0901b87e96c14c66a77a925333f8afe2.mp4?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By destroying enemies, you gain experience and credits, which you can use to pump up your characteristics and buy items.Improving your character is an important part of your adventure. With enhanced skills, you'll be able to take down enemies faster, hack weapon crates, earn more credits, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/ec54c5c47148aa0c410ed91ab057a2b5.poster.avif?t=1760799085\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/ec54c5c47148aa0c410ed91ab057a2b5.webm?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469130/extras/ec54c5c47148aa0c410ed91ab057a2b5.mp4?t=1760799085\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dexterity is your middle name, and on the battlefield you'll have to show it to the fullest, dodging enemy fire. Use swipes and jumps to outsmart the enemy and come at him from behind, and then victory will be yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
